34
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,920
Got it.

35
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:24,110
Just go fighting him.

36
00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:25,910
I'll transfer all my Dou Qi to you

37
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:26,960
