56
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,160
Luckily, the Emperor Seal Technique
helped a lot.

57
00:03:49,390 --> 00:03:51,190
But it's a special technique of Gu Clan.

58
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:53,240
It shouldn't be…

59
