Headmaster.

63
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,030
Headmaster.

64
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:12,160
Today,

65
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:16,230
you've done a much better job

66
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,200
than in Strong Ranking Grand Competitions.

67
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,110
Headmaster,

68
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:23,230
we will protect Jia Nan Academy.

69
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,880
Hall of Souls bounces back.

70
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,550
As Dou Practitioners,

71
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,270
you must fight for the world's sake.

72
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:39,070
Hu Qian,

73
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,760
take care of

74
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,480
the Academy

75
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,550
and these kids.

76
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,000
Headmaster.

77
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:55,600
- Headmaster.
- Headmaster.

78
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,560
Headmaster.

79
00:04:58,790 --> 00:04:59,630
Headmaster.

80
00:05:00,790 --> 00:05:01,830
Headmaster.

81
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,070
Headmaster.

82
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,200
Detach the Fallen Heart Flame?

83
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,510
Why should it be detached?

84
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:20,110
It belongs to Jia Nan Academy.

85
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:22,110
It underpins
the Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower.

86
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,160
It fuels students' practice.

87
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,000
I borrowed it from Headmaster

88
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:28,200
to save my father from Misty Cloud Sect.

89
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,200
The murder of my father has been avenged,

90
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,720
so, I should return it to the Academy.

91
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,040
This is what I owe the Academy.

92
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:37,000
It can't be detached from you.

93
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,600
Otherwise, you're dead.

94
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,950
Flame Mantra can conquer the flame.

95
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,550
It will detach it as well.

96
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,880
Besides, no one knows it

97
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,110
better than you.

98
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:47,720
Your guidance will guarantee success.

99
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,480
Promise me that

100
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:55,070
the newly detached Fallen Heart Flame

101
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,320
must still be guarded by me.

102
00:05:58,830 --> 00:05:59,670
OK,

103
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,350
I promise on behalf of Headmaster Hu Qian.

104
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,160
It's time.

105
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,040
Headmaster Su Qian,

106
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:59,110
I'm giving it back to the Academy.

107
00:07:06,550 --> 00:07:07,390
Look.

108
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,760
It's Fallen Heart Flame.

109
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,600
Look.

110
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:14,950
Fallen Heart Flame.

111
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,320
Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower

112
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:19,040
is equipped with Fallen Heart Flame now.

113
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:22,270
Only with Fallen Heart Flame can the Academy

114
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,950
be called Jia Nan Academy.

115
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,440
(The extreme heat of Magma World)

116
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:47,270
(and the refining by Fallen Heart Flame)

117
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,950
(can temporarily)

118
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:52,760
(suppress the once-active Woeful Poison Body)

119
00:07:53,230 --> 00:07:55,720
(and keep it stable.)

120
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,790
How long can it hold on?

121
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,790
It's hard to say.

122
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,160
In such as case,

123
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:04,480
it will be unstable once she leaves here.

124
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:07,790
(It's better to find Bodhisattva Saliva ASAP)

125
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,790
(to address the problem.)

126
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:25,390
Be honest if you don't know.

127
00:08:25,670 --> 00:08:28,040
Don't lie to me that they've perished.

128
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,320
Who said I don't know?

129
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:37,230
Then tell me what happened exactly.

130
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,080
Bodhisattva Trees

131
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:44,760
never grew in isolation.

132
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:48,150
They were distributed
across the Dou Qi Continent

133
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:51,080
in rarely-visited places.

134
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,520
Their entwined roots

135
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,910
reached thousands of miles underground,

136
00:08:57,280 --> 00:09:00,760
forming an underground palace.

137
00:09:01,230 --> 00:09:03,110
Their energy flows

138
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:06,400
traveled around the whole Dou Qi Continent.

139
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,280
Were they really that powerful?

140
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:17,400
It's a pity that 50 years ago,

141
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,000
they died away suddenly.

142
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:22,080
People speculated

143
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:25,590
it had something to do
with the Hall of Souls.

144
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,520
Hall of Souls?

145
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,640
Anyway, it's useless even if you go there.

146
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:32,760
They have withered,
so there's no Bodhisattva Heart.

147
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,470
Let along Bodhisattva Saliva.

148
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,030
Please take me there

149
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,320
if you truly know.

150
00:09:41,230 --> 00:09:42,070
No way.

151
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:42,950
Why not?

152
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:45,960
I've been in this tower for a long time.

153
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:49,080
All my skills and techniques

154
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,320
are integrated into this tower.

155
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,080
In other words,

156
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,350
in this tower,

157
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:58,710
I'm respected as Flame Sage.

158
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,710
Outside the tower,

159
00:10:01,230 --> 00:10:02,960
I will simply become

160
00:10:03,230 --> 00:10:05,670
an old man of no use.

161
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,720
I got it.

162
00:10:09,110 --> 00:10:10,150
You don't know.

163
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,360
You're lying.

164
00:10:12,470 --> 00:10:13,310
What?

165
00:10:13,710 --> 00:10:14,790
Who's lying?

166
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,670
I'm going to take you there now.

167
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,080
Apologize to me

168
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:19,550
if they do wither.

169
00:10:27,350 --> 00:10:30,880
You're desperate for Bodhisattva Saliva.

170
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:34,590
Do you like that girl?

171
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:36,640
Who? Little Fairy Doctor?

172
00:10:37,230 --> 00:10:38,350
She's my friend.

173
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,750
Friend?

174
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,590
Oh, no, no.

175
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:44,400
You can't see or touch her.

176
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:46,200
It's of no use

177
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,280
even if

178
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,760
you find the antidote.

179
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,800
Why?

180
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,760
Bodhisattva Saliva

181
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:55,350
must be applied to naked bodies.

182
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,030
You're joking.

183
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,240
I'm not joking.

184
00:10:58,580 --> 00:10:59,430
Fine,

185
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,470
believe it or not.

186
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:13,000
See?

187
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:14,640
This is a Bodhisattva Tree.

188
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,840
Bodhisattva Trees

189
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:21,550
produced the strongest energy
on the Dou Qi Continent.

190
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,670
But they are no longer alive.

191
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:28,520
Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.

192
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,440
It's still standing straight here.

193
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,000
Who said it's dead?

194
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,590
It's the same as death, isn't it?

195
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,470
Kid, you see the tree now.

196
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:52,720
Apologize to me.

197
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,960
You must apologize to me.

198
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:04,750
What are you doing?

199
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:10,400
It's a sacred tree from ancient times.

200
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,670
Could it have a heart as well?

201
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:16,350
If I try my heart flame on it,

202
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:19,520
could it be revived?

203
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,320
No.

204
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:24,640
No one is able to revive it.

205
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:28,280
The way you mobilize the flame

206
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:30,400
costs a lot of Dou Qi.

207
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,910
If this tree is not helpful,

208
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:34,640
I can find another tree in Central Plains.

209
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,350
I must find Bodhisattva Saliva.

210
00:12:38,470 --> 00:12:39,310
It's of no use.

211
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,670
Don't waste your energy.

212
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,790
This is the stronghold
of the Black Submerged Army.

213
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,000
Gu Hao, Evil General,

214
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,790
pays respect to Clan Lady and Devil General.

215
00:13:05,230 --> 00:13:06,840
This is the Bodhisattva Tree.

216
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:10,000
I heard they were all over Dou Qi Continent

217
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,120
and shared the same root.

218
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,320
When Hun Miesheng was sealed here,

219
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,550
all the trees on the Dou Qi Continent

220
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:16,710
became withered.

221
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:18,310
Yeah.

222
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:20,320
If we want to enter the tree

223
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,440
to check the seal,

224
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:22,960
we need to trigger the energy of the tree.

225
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,230
What's this?

226
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,800
Where's he?

227
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:33,520
There's a Bodhisattva Tree inside the tree!

228
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:13,110
Are you asking me to refine the seed with flame

229
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,520
to dissolve negative feelings?

230
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:41,240
It's working.

231
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,790
Is this the remains of Hun Miesheng?

232
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:19,240
Yes.

233
00:16:19,710 --> 00:16:22,000
He was a Demi Dou Saint before dying.

234
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,400
During the past 50 years,
his flesh was decayed,

235
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,480
but not his skeletons.

236
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,590
So, Gu Clan can't let the guard down.

237
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,350
The hexagram is the sign of our seal.

238
00:16:36,350 --> 00:16:37,230
No, I can't hold on.

239
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:39,310
I'm so tired.

240
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,430
All finished now.

241
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:55,160
Bodhisattva Heart?

242
00:17:58,280 --> 00:17:59,950
Bodhisattva Hearts are in Bodhisattva Trees.

243
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,360
The tears shed by Bodhisattva Hearts

244
00:18:02,710 --> 00:18:04,400
are Bodhisattva Saliva.

245
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,280
Around the world,

246
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,710
only Dao is to be revered.

247
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,070
The shining golden light

248
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,680
covers my body.

249
00:18:28,190 --> 00:18:29,310
Evil spirits are suppressed

250
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:30,830
and unable to be revived.

251
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,350
You reach the Dou Venerate level.

252
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:51,950
Brother,

253
00:18:52,710 --> 00:18:54,880
you're still good at sensing.

254
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,640
The travel is worthwhile.

255
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:04,430
Why don't you ask me

256
00:19:04,430 --> 00:19:06,350
from whom I absorbed Dou Qi?

257
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:35,680
It seems Xiao Yan

258
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,920
resisted the attack again.

259
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,950
He's just lucky.

260
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:44,680
He was unable to save Su Qian.

261
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:47,920
Did you kill Su Qian?

262
00:19:48,470 --> 00:19:50,920
His Dou Qi was pure and intense.

263
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,950
It helped me break the bottleneck at once

264
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:55,110
and return to Dou Venerate level.

265
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:58,190
So,

266
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:00,350
you didn't win over Xiao Yan.

267
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,520
It seems

268
00:20:03,190 --> 00:20:05,190
you have to wait longer for your formation.

269
00:20:06,350 --> 00:20:09,110
There's not just one flame in the world.

270
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:19,430
The black and white one

271
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,760
is Yin-Yang Twin Flame ranked 21.

272
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:24,710
The green one

273
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:27,920
is Ghostly Poison Flame ranked 20.

274
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:32,310
I sent Han Feng to Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower

275
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:35,310
for Fallen Heart Flame ranked 14.

276
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:38,920
But instead of capturing it,

277
00:20:39,190 --> 00:20:40,880
he found you.

278
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,760
If I get Bone Spirit Cold Flame,

279
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,920
I can achieve my goal immediately.

280
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:50,000
I set the trap in Misty Cloud Sect

281
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:52,520
for your Bone Spirit Cold Flame.

